/**Project name: NS sample radio development                                            */
/*Process name : Startup   	                                            				*/
/*File name    : Initial transaction of perimeter I/O register 			        		*/
/*Outline      : Initialize port and register  	                                        */
/*Function     : Startup by reset interruption                                          */
/*Returned value: None                                                                  */
/*Argument      : None                                                                  */
/*Input-output  : None                                                                  */
/*Version       : v00.00 2002/09/25 1st edition by M.Kaneko                             */
/*   Copyright (C) 2002 Development Division of NIIGATA SEIMITSU                        */
